[[File:Hivegallery.jpg|thumb|right|[[Archduke/Legends|Archduke]] [[Poggle the Lesser/Legends|Poggle the Lesser]] takes [[Dooku/Legends|Count Dooku]] and the [[Separatist Council/Legends|Separatist Council]] on a tour of one of the [[Geonosian/Legends|Geonosian]] hive galleries of [[Stalgasin hive/Legends|Stalgasin hive]].]]

The '''Geonosian hive gallery''' was located in the [[Geonosis droid factories/Legends|Geonosis droid foundries]] entrance tower. It was there where [[Obi-Wan Kenobi/Legends|Obi-Wan Kenobi]] had discovered that [[Viceroy/Legends|Viceroy]] [[Nute Gunray/Legends|Nute Gunray]] was behind the assassination attempts on [[Senator/Legends|Senator]] [[Padmé Amidala/Legends|Padmé Amidala's]] life.

